From: Developer <dev@example.com>
Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add built-in CSRF protection mechanism

This patch adds native CSRF protection to Flask, providing:
- Double-submit cookie pattern
- Origin/Referer header validation
- Template integration with csrf_token() and csrf_input()
- Configurable exempt routes
- Secure defaults (SameSite=Lax, Secure=True)

---
 src/flask/__init__.py   |   4 +
 src/flask/app.py        |  12 ++
 src/flask/csrf.py       | 287 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/flask/templating.py |   8 ++
 4 files changed, 311 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 src/flask/csrf.py

